Bg7 5. h4 dxc4 6. e4 c5 7. d5 b5 8. h5 Nxh5 (8... b4 $6 9. h6 $1 {White closes
the "h" file, but it is more important to kick away the black bishop from the
so vital long diagonal.} Bf8 10. Na4 (10. e5 bxc3 11. exf6 exf6 12. Bxc4 cxb2
13. Bxb2 Bd6 14. Qe2+ Qe7 15. Qxe7+ Kxe7 16. O-O {with great initiative even
